name: Superseding chapters
text:
SUPERSEDING CHAPTERS
 
         [2008 amendment retroactive to July 1, 2006.  L 2008, c 28, §43.]  In the event of any conflict between the provisions of this chapter and the provisions of chapter 421J, 514A, 514B, or 514E, the provisions of chapter 421J, 514A, 514B, or 514E shall supersede and control the provisions of this chapter. [L 2002, c 130, §3; am L 2004, c 164, §11; am L 2005, c 93, §7; am L 2008, c 28, §8]
